A mobile app for medicine

Here is the MVP:

Core Features (MVP)
1. Medication Schedule & Tracker
List of daily medications

Mark as “Taken” or “Skipped”

Dosage, frequency, and time reminders

Icons or photos of pills for easy recognition

2. Smart Reminders
Push notifications with:
“Time to take your 8 AM medication: Metformin 500mg”

Voice assistant integration for accessibility

3. Refill Alerts
Alert user when refills are running low (e.g., 3 days of pills left)

Optional “Request Refill” button tied to pharmacy contact info

4. Medication Detail View
Pill color, shape, imprint

Dosage instructions

Doctor’s notes or warnings

5. Daily Summary Screen
“You have taken 3/5 medications today”

Simple color-coded dashboard
